@prefix orion: <http://conjourney.net/orion#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

orion:CognitiveTrace a rdfs:Class .
orion:ReasoningTrace a rdfs:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf orion:CognitiveTrace .
orion:PlanTrace a rdfs:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf orion:CognitiveTrace .
orion:ReflectionTrace a rdfs:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf orion:CognitiveTrace .
orion:SelfCritique a rdfs:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf orion:CognitiveTrace .

orion:traceOfTurn a rdf:Property .
orion:traceInfluences a rdf:Property .
orion:generatedByModel a rdf:Property .
orion:traceStage a rdf:Property .
